OL,3,CMum shares grief over second Christmas
OL,4,Cwithout her son's murder being solved
OL,6,FA mum has said her life "feels
OL,7,Fpointless" as she prepares for a
OL,8,Fsecond Christmas without her son who
OL,9,Fwas shot dead.
OL,11,FEllis Cox, 19, was shot and killed on
OL,12,F23 June 2024 at the Liver Industrial
OL,13,FEstate in Merseyside while returning
OL,14,Fhome from a bike ride.
OL,16,FThe teenager was with with four others
OL,17,Fon the Loop Line before they were
OL,18,Fapproached by "one to three males on
OL,19,Ftwo electric bikes" at around 10:50pm.
