OL,3,CMum shares grief over second Christmas
OL,4,Cwithout her son's murder being solved
OL,6,FOne of the group fired three shots at
OL,7,FEllis and his group. He attempted to
OL,8,Fleave, but was shot in the back.
OL,10,FDetectives have made six arrests in
OL,11,Fconnection with the murder but no one
OL,12,Fhas been charged.
OL,14,FThe Loop Line is a path which is
OL,15,Fheavily overgrown and dimly lit. The
OL,16,Fsuspects were not captured on CCTV.
OL,18,FCarolyn Cox and Julie O'Toole, the mum
OL,19,Fand auntie of Ellis, are trying to
OL,20,Fkeep the investigation in the
OL,21,Fspotlight.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
