OL,3,CMum shares grief over second Christmas
OL,4,Cwithout her son's murder being solved
OL,6,FAhead of the second Christmas without
OL,7,Fhim, Carolyn addressed her grief in a
OL,8,Fletter to her son. She said: "The pain
OL,9,Fis still as raw as it was the day you
OL,10,Fwere taken from us.
OL,12,F"We keep waiting for time to soften
OL,13,Fit, but it hasn't. It's only taught us
OL,14,Fhow to survive with a piece of our
OL,15,Fhearts missing.
OL,17,F"It's so hard knowing we won't get to
OL,18,Ftake any more pictures with you, or
OL,19,Fshare special dates and milestones. So
OL,20,Fmuch of it all feels pointless without
OL,21,Fyou here.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
