OL,3,CMum shares grief over second Christmas
OL,4,Cwithout her son's murder being solved
OL,6,FShe said: "We're being strong for each
OL,7,Fother, because we have to be. And
OL,8,Fsomehow, in the quiet moments, we know
OL,9,Fyou walk beside us. We feel you. We
OL,10,Fdream of you. You're never far, even
OL,11,Fwhen the ache feels unbearable.
OL,13,F"You were robbed of a beautiful life -
OL,14,Fof the plans you were going to make,
OL,15,Fthe mark you were going to leave on
OL,16,Fthis world, and all the places you
OL,17,Fwere meant to see.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
