OL,3,CMum shares grief over second Christmas
OL,4,Cwithout her son's murder being solved
OL,6,F"You would have done great things,
OL,7,FEllis. We know it. And we would have
OL,8,Fbeen right there beside you for every
OL,9,Fstep.
OL,11,F"You were everything to us. You still
OL,12,Fare. Every step we take, we take with
OL,13,Fyou in our minds. Nothing will ever be
OL,14,Fthe same again without you ` the
OL,15,Fdevastation cuts too deep.
OL,17,F"Our pain has become our driver and
OL,18,Fgetting justice for you It's what gets
OL,19,Fus out of bed each day. It's what
OL,20,Fkeeps us going when everything inside
OL,21,Fwants to stop."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
